“Hi everyone, I’m Vasudha 🐄✨
Elder sister to Vrinda — and maybe a little too protective sometimes 🙈
But that’s what love looks like when it’s wrapped in care.
I may not speak your language, but I feel everything —
Joy, love, and even the silence of those I care for.
My heart is big, my eyes are gentle,
And my presence? Always there, like the quiet strength of an elder sister.
In this Gokul Family, I’m not just a cow…
I’m a heartbeat. A guardian. A soft shoulder with strong hooves. 💛
.
.
